Baskin Financial Services Inc. Buys Vail Resorts, FirstService, Fortis


February 06, 2017, 01:38:04 PM EDT
By insider, GuruFocus









































Shutterstock photo


Baskin Financial Services Inc.New Purchases: MTN , FTS ,Added Positions: FSV , AAPL, KAR, DIS, V, MCO, DPS, PCLN, ZBH, BAM,Reduced Positions:VIAB, JPM, CVS, GS, TEVA,For the details of Baskin Financial Services Inc.'s stock buys and sells, go to http://www.gurufocus.com/StockBuy.php?GuruName=Baskin+Financial+Services+Inc.These are the top 5 holdings of Baskin Financial Services Inc.Apple Inc ( AAPL ) - 182,820 shares, 5.21% of the total portfolio. Shares added by 5.61%Alphabet Inc ( GOOG ) - 22,180 shares, 4.21% of the total portfolio. Shares added by 1.35%Brookfield Asset Management Inc ( BAM ) - 506,502 shares, 4.11% of the total portfolio. Shares added by 2.98%Brookfield Infrastructure Partners LP ( BIP ) - 498,904 shares, 4.09% of the total portfolio. Shares added by 1.42%JPMorgan Chase & Co ( JPM ) - 182,076 shares, 3.87% of the total portfolio. Shares reduced by 1.2%New Purchase: Vail Resorts Inc (MTN)Baskin Financial Services Inc. initiated holdings in Vail Resorts Inc. The purchase prices were between $153.19 and $167.99, with an estimated average price of $158.8. The stock is now traded at around $173.94. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 2%. The holdings were 50,311 shares as of 2016-12-31.New Purchase: Fortis Inc (FTS)Baskin Financial Services Inc. initiated holdings in Fortis Inc. The purchase prices were between $29.4 and $33.25, with an estimated average price of $31.03. The stock is now traded at around $31.85. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 0.26%. The holdings were 34,757 shares as of 2016-12-31.Added: FirstService Corp (FSV)Baskin Financial Services Inc. added to the holdings in FirstService Corp by 20.86%. The purchase prices were between $39.4 and $47.69, with an estimated average price of $43.77. The stock is now traded at around $49.78. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 0.33%. The holdings were 165,235 shares as of 2016-12-31.Added: Wells Fargo & Co (WFC)Baskin Financial Services Inc. added to the holdings in Wells Fargo & Co by 21.66%. The purchase prices were between $43.75 and $57.29, with an estimated average price of $50.28. The stock is now traded at around $56.77. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 0.02%. The holdings were 6,739 shares as of 2016-12-31.Added: Canadian National Railway Co (CNI)Baskin Financial Services Inc. added to the holdings in Canadian National Railway Co by 23.79%. The purchase prices were between $61.95 and $69.85, with an estimated average price of $66.01. The stock is now traded at around $68.51. The impact to the portfolio due to this purchase was 0.02%. The holdings were 7,416 shares as of 2016-12-31.Warning! GuruFocus has detected 6 Warning Signs with FSV. Click here to check it out.FSV 15-Year Financial DataThe intrinsic value of FSVPeter Lynch Chart of FSVPremium MembersThis article first appeared on GuruFocus .



